      <!-- Article Content -->
      <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        
        <h2>What is ProProfs Chat?</h2>
        
        <p>ProProfs Chat is a comprehensive live chat software solution designed for businesses of all sizes. Launched in 2005, it has grown to serve over 1 million users worldwide, making it one of the established players in the live chat industry.</p>

        <p>The platform focuses on providing reliable, feature-rich live chat functionality with an emphasis on ease of use and affordability. Unlike some competitors that target only enterprise customers, ProProfs Chat offers solutions for small businesses, mid-market companies, and large enterprises.</p>

        <h2>Key Features and Capabilities</h2>

        <h3>Live Chat Functionality</h3>
        
        <p>At its core, ProProfs Chat provides robust live chat capabilities:</p>
        
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Real-time Messaging:</strong> Instant communication between visitors and support agents</li>
          <li><strong>Chat Routing:</strong> Automatic distribution of chats to available agents</li>
          <li><strong>Canned Responses:</strong> Pre-written responses for common questions</li>
          <li><strong>File Sharing:</strong> Share documents, images, and files during conversations</li>
          <li><strong>Chat Transcripts:</strong> Complete conversation history and records</li>
          <li><strong>Visitor Information:</strong> Real-time visitor details and browsing behavior</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Customization Options</h3>
        
        <p>ProProfs Chat offers several customization features:</p>
        
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Chat Widget Design:</strong> Customize colors, position, and appearance</li>
          <li><strong>Branding:</strong> Add your logo and brand colors</li>
          <li><strong>Welcome Messages:</strong> Personalized greetings for different pages</li>
          <li><strong>Operating Hours:</strong> Set availability schedules</li>
          <li><strong>Offline Forms:</strong> Capture leads when agents are unavailable</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Analytics and Reporting</h3>
        
        <p>The platform provides comprehensive analytics:</p>
        
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Chat Volume Reports:</strong> Track conversation trends over time</li>
          <li><strong>Agent Performance:</strong> Monitor response times and satisfaction scores</li>
          <li><strong>Visitor Analytics:</strong> Understand visitor behavior and patterns</li>
          <li><strong>Conversion Tracking:</strong> Measure chat impact on sales and goals</li>
          <li><strong>Custom Reports:</strong> Create tailored reports for specific metrics</li>
        </ul>

