        <ul>
          <li><strong>Clean Layout:</strong> Intuitive interface with easy navigation</li>
          <li><strong>Multi-chat Management:</strong> Handle multiple conversations simultaneously</li>
          <li><strong>Visitor Queue:</strong> See waiting visitors and their information</li>
          <li><strong>Quick Actions:</strong> Fast access to common functions</li>
          <li><strong>Real-time Notifications:</strong> Instant alerts for new chats</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Visitor Experience</h3>
        
        <p>From the visitor's perspective, ProProfs Chat offers:</p>
        
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Fast Loading:</strong> Lightweight chat widget that doesn't slow down websites</li>
          <li><strong>Mobile Responsive:</strong> Works seamlessly on all devices</li>
          <li><strong>Easy to Use:</strong> Simple interface that requires no learning curve</li>
          <li><strong>File Sharing:</strong> Ability to share screenshots and documents</li>
